
'''''Funeral for an Assassin''''' ni filime yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] yasohotse muri 1974 iyobowe na Ivan Hall yasohotse muri [[Amerika]] mu 1977<ref>https://www.encyclopedia.com/arts/culture-magazines/funeral-assassin</ref><ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/funeral-for-an-assassin/</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Michael Cardiff numuntu uharanira impinduramatwara wabigize umwuga watojwe cyane muburyo butandukanye bwo kwica<ref>https://www.originalfilmart.com/products/funeral-for-an-assassin-1974</ref><ref>https://spicyonion.com/title/funeral-for-an-assassin-english-movie/</ref>, gucengera no guhunga amategeko. Amaze gutoroka gereza ashyira ibintu bimuranga ku mubiri wangiritse kugira ngo agaragare ko yapfuye mu gihe ateganya kwihimura kuri guverinoma<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/131963-funeral-for-an-assassin</ref>. Cardiff akoresha ubuhanga bwe mu kwica umucamanza ukomeye bituma urupfu rwe rusa nkimpanuka kugirango atere ibikoresho biturika bitunguranye mu muhango wo kumushyingura witabiriwe n’abimuka n’abanyeganyeza ubutegetsi<ref>https://impdb.fandom.com/wiki/Funeral_for_an_Assassin</ref>. Gusa kapiteni wa polisi udahuje ibitekerezo ari kuri gahunda ze.<ref>https://movies.alphacoders.com/movies/view/27865/Funeral-for-an-Assassin</ref><ref>https://www.tvguide.com/movies/funeral-for-an-assassin/2000110248/</ref>

